title: Meta Junglers.
body:
Just thought if post some junglers I thought would be helpful to some that I think a really strong at the moment.
Diana
Nunu
Warwick
Kayle
Rek'sai
Pantheon 
Amumu
Nocturne.

If anyone has someone else they would like to add please do so.

replies.body: post nerf WW and panth still top of the pops?
idgaf, let the jungle mains sort this sh!t out, I don't want people new to the jungle trying these champs in ranked, if u aren't a jungler just GTFO.
Vi, Lee, Kha and Elise are all good picks assuming you go Ranger's Trailblazer like a human and have some idea of how to Jungle.
